snippet.title: Minecraft 1.19 Hardcore Let's Play: Medieval Mob Farm! Episode 3
snippet.description:

Let's Play Hardcore Minecraft 1.19 Episode 3! In this episode we build a large medieval mob farm so we can get an abundance of mob drops for our early game! I used complementary shaders when recording this episode!! I hope that all of these videos can help people out there sleep, relax, and study!
